      "content": "Maintaining \"current state\" on failing hardware is a direct violation of safety protocols. If the local server hardware fails before the migration is complete, the station loses all monitoring capability. \n\nPlease clarify: if you do not migrate to the cloud, how do you plan to ensure the continuity of the meteorological data once this local hardware reaches its end-of-life?",
